snippet.title: Amber Heard Biography (Age, Affairs, Breast Size etc)
snippet.description:
Amber Laura Heard (born April 22, 1986)[3] is an American actress and model. Born and raised in Texas, Heard made her film debut in a minor supporting role in the sports drama Friday Night Lights (2004), followed by a series of other small roles in television and film.
